evaluation.response:
Glad to hear your photo shoot turned out well!

It sounds like you might be facing a mental hurdle. Weight fluctuations are normal and can fluctuate daily depending on how much water you intake and digest. Meal “X” / day “Y” won’t single-handedly erase your progress. 

This work is understandably additive. I definitely recommend scheduling a check in with your mentor to unpack the working script of hunger with appropriate amount.&#x20;
